title: BBC Sportscene  SPFL 720p 50fps 03.12.2017
description:
Introduced by Jonathan Sutherland.   
 
Highlights of the weekend's Scottish Premiership action, with Sunday's Aberdeen versus Rangers match at Pittodrie taking top billing. It's their first meeting since May last season, when the Dons secured victory at Ibrox for the first time since 1991.   
 
Among Saturday's games, Celtic host Motherwell in a repeat of last weekend's League Cup final, while Hibernian are in Glasgow to play Partick Thistle.

Audio : AAC, 48 KHz, 96 kbps
